msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Nintendo Entertainment System, also known as the Famicom (for \"Family Computer\"), was released in 1983. The cross-shaped directional pad was designed for Game & Watch systems, replacing the bulkier joysticks found on earlier controllers."
msgstr "Il Nintendo Entertainment System, noto anche come Famicom (per \"Family Computer\"), fu lanciato nel 1983. Il pad direzionale a forma di croce fu progettato per i sistemi Game & Watch, in sostituzione dei joystick più ingombranti presenti sui controller precedenti."

